Package com.paypal.selion.platform.html.support.events

Contains the customized event strategy for web elements.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Checkable
    Interface for elements which can be checked.
    Clickable
    Interface for elements which can be clicked.
    Deselectable
    Interface for elements which can be deselected.
    ElementEventListener
    Events which can occur in SeLion's AbstractElement implementations.
    Hoverable
    A marker Interface that represents those elements upon which the hover action can be performed.
    Selectable
    Interface for elements which can be selected.
    Submitable
    Interface for elements which perform a submit action.
    Typeable
    Interface for elements which can receive text input.
    Uncheckable
    Interface for elements which can be unchecked.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractElementEventListener
    Use this class as base class, if you want to implement a ElementEventListener and are only interested in some events.
